{"tid":298811,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"再次證明王晶只係一件垃圾","createTime":"2017-06-26T14:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T15:40:49.000Z","uid":34571,"like":364,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"762f5bc31c8cf10c6cd7d8af267e53e2b51219b5","tid":298811,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T14:38:40.000Z","msg":"TVB 押咁重落套賭城群英會, 將佢當係重頭劇咁宣傳,<br />\n咁信王晶, 以為會幫TVB拍套有電影感既好劇吸收視<br />\n結果, 一如既往, 係一套垃圾, 劇情垃圾, 低俗, 完全合乎王晶電影既style<br />\n其實咁多年黎, 王晶既電影大部份都係低俗為主, 情節不足, 就揾一大班明星朋友去彌補, 例如, 最近既賭城風雲三步曲又係無厘頭電影, 入場人士都係因為主角係幾位影帝而受到吸引<br />\n<br />\n所以王晶只係電影界沽名釣譽既一個肥佬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20151230/s00001/1451443944853SL4_15EC567A89CF3F0E1CF0072FE27230B7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20151230%2Fs00001%2F1451443944853SL4_15EC567A89CF3F0E1CF0072FE27230B7.jpg&h=530e2c3e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e61971c338b232763ab7553db4e035bd1d2cac89","tid":298811,"uid":34571,"like":5,"dislike":14,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T14:39:43.000Z","msg":"利申返, 係屋企人開住電視睇TVB, 我依個時間係睇緊達哥, 其實近年屋企人都只係慣咗開住有聲"},{"pid":"32c252ee41025054d549eabadef79ab2fae1176d","tid":298811,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T14:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fa32100b9981146104b76624576466f252f17c6","tid":298811,"uid":60982,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T14:53:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申返, 係屋企人開住電視睇TVB, 我依個時間係睇緊達哥, 其實近年屋企人都只係慣咗開住有聲</blockquote><br />\n個頭盔硬撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e010362eba16a0d98b2cb813a3d648a32b337c4","tid":298811,"uid":7699,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T14:53:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申返, 係屋企人開住電視睇TVB, 我依個時間係睇緊達哥, 其實近年屋企人都只係慣咗開住有聲</blockquote><br />\n9點半睇隔